name: rules
title: RULES
description:
• No shit-talking or fighting please! I'm trying to make this a soft and friendly server
• No pedophilia, racism, and homophobia. Any form of prejudice against someones beliefs and who they are will be perma banned.
• NSFW stuff stays in the NSFW chat. It does say 18+ to enter but anyone who is mature and 16+ can enter that channel.
• PLEASE don't fight over Mudae! There are no rules set for that since it is a game based off of chance. If someone gets the character you want, kindly ask if they want to trade– don't be an asshole about it.
•Don't spam mention Moderators or me please!
